{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783486597447,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66afffetpkX52bffjbY3h","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_8d1EfXY9ljgBUk7s0hgCO1yk","state":{"status":"error","input":{"prompt":"You are orchestrating the deep-research workflow YAML as a detached fan-out lineage.\nThis is an explicit parallel-detached OpenCode lineage, not a self-invocation of the parent session.\nUse the separate lineage directory and session id below as the detached state boundary.\n\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md and execute the research loop with these parameters:\n  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4\n  session_id: fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\n  loop_type: research\n  config.stopPolicy: convergence\n  research_topic: Validate and stress-test the merge design for folding deep-loop-runtime into deep-loop-workflows as system-deep-loop: structural layout, bidirectional path-coupling repair, the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow, reference migration across commands/agents/READMEs/advisor-corpus, and whether fallback-router.ts should be wired for real GLM-5.2 to MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback.\n  config.maxIterations: 10\nThe step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4 via the\nconfig.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\ncommand; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\n\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop (to legal convergence OR config.maxIterations, whichever comes first), and phase_synthesis.\nWrite all outputs to .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4. Do not touch any path outside .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-4","specFolder":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":5,"session_id":"fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":true},"error":"MCP error -32000: Connection closed","time":{"start":1783486562387,"end":1783486597444}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0b9ad08f0149b232016a4dd858cc048191b427ec3ea0f32309"}},"id":"prt_f40151b1e001AkLlanCy6f3bvK","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66afffetpkX52bffjbY3h","messageID":"msg_f40149ea6001yHOfZ6E1if59hA"}}
