{"type":"text","timestamp":1783486646751,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66afffetpkX52bffjbY3h","part":{"id":"prt_f40168556001EdvEswqtr3097j","messageID":"msg_f40167f360017ya2KWlnapi3su","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66afffetpkX52bffjbY3h","type":"text","text":"I’ve found the YAML branch for `cli-opencode`, but this request explicitly says this is already a detached OpenCode lineage and not a parent self-invocation. I’ll execute the loop in-line against the externalized files rather than recursively launching `opencode run` from OpenCode.","time":{"start":1783486645590,"end":1783486646749},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_02d2e9c9618eb52f016a4dd8b598cc8191b4037e9f77b040cf","phase":"commentary"}}}}
