{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1783486772342,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66afffetpkX52bffjbY3h","part":{"id":"prt_f40187475001YVS7FUbtCMIYs3","messageID":"msg_f40186fc80017BsmCm23Se920l","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66afffetpkX52bffjbY3h","snapshot":"9b938210f9504fb2b8c45bbbb50bc26f1ba120a2","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"text","timestamp":1783486775233,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66afffetpkX52bffjbY3h","part":{"id":"prt_f40187ea0001hev5GiEI0fp3qW","messageID":"msg_f40186fc80017BsmCm23Se920l","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66afffetpkX52bffjbY3h","type":"text","text":"I found one discrepancy in the existing design: `runtime/package.json` is already self-contained for runtime deps, but its `typecheck` and `tsconfig` still borrow TypeScript/@types from `system-spec-kit`. That means the merge plan should keep the lightweight tooling-borrow path repair, not describe the whole runtime as dependency-self-contained.","time":{"start":1783486774944,"end":1783486775231},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_04a20bc123d7f7ff016a4dd936f0b48191a9fb973b2fd5df5c","phase":"commentary"}}}}
