\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"The package already owns runtime dependencies, but typecheck/typeRoots and system-spec-kit test discovery still need depth repair after nesting.\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Fully decouple TypeScript tooling during the structural move\",\"reason\":\"The phase docs intentionally keep decoupling out of scope so merge failures and decoupling failures remain distinguishable.\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/plan.md:99\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T05:20:00Z\",\"durationMs\":300000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"sourcePaths\":[\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/package.json\",\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tsconfig.json\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/package.json\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/vitest.config.ts\"]}\n+{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":3,\"run\":3,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research execution=single_iteration\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"External reference migration across commands, agents, READMEs, hooks, plugin, and advisor corpus\",\"findingsCount\":4,\"newInfoRatio\":0.52,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Mostly confirmed the Stage C-J sequencing, with extra emphasis on paired Python/TypeScript advisor constants and projection-hash regeneration.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Does the external migration plan cover all high-risk reference surfaces?\",\"Are advisor-corpus edits safely scoped?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"The migration plan correctly separates hardcoded constants, generated projections, compiled command contracts, prose, graph edges, and corpus rebaseline.\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Blind repository-wide replacement of old skill ids\",\"reason\":\"Advisor corpus and divergence ledger need field-scoped replaceme