complete\",\"focus\":\"Fallback-router wiring decision and fanout retry seam\",\"findingsCount\":3,\"newInfoRatio\":0.34,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Confirmed the zero-caller gap and identified a safer integration seam than putting model policy inside the generic pool primitive.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Should fallback-router.ts become a merge blocker?\",\"Where should fallback substitution be wired if the optional phase runs?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Fallback wiring should remain optional for the structural merge; if implemented, fanout-run should own model policy and pass a retry-exhausted hook to the generic pool.\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Embed a hardcoded GLM to MiMo registry directly in fanout-pool.cjs\",\"reason\":\"fanout-pool.cjs is a generic worker-pool primitive and currently only knows items, retry counts, worker, and ledger callbacks.\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/fanout-pool.cjs:418\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T05:30:00Z\",\"durationMs\":300000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"sourcePaths\":[\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/fallback-router.ts\",\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tests/unit/fallback-router.vitest.ts\",\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/fanout-pool.cjs\",\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/fanout-run.cjs\"]}\n+{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":5,\"run\":5,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research execution=single_iteration\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Final stress test, verification ordering, and residual risks\",\"findingsCount\":2,\"newInfoRatio\":0.12,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Final pass mostly consolidated prior findings; only minor sequencing risks remained after all key questions had evidence-backed answers.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"What verification gates should block closeout?\",\"Are any merge-plan risks still unresolved?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"The closeout gates need runtime tests, system-spec-kit council tests, advisor accuracy rebaseline, divergence ratchet, mirror sync, residual grep, and temporary-symlink removal before any completion claim.\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Leave compatibility symlinks through final verification\",\"reason\":\"The parent success criteria require old top-level skill folders gone and residual grep clean outside allowlists.\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/spec.md:100\"}],\"convergenceSignals\":{\"rollingAvg\":0.3267,\"madNoiseFloor\":0.4448,\"entropyCoverage\":1.0,\"compositeStop\":0.7},\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T05:35:00Z\",\"durationMs\":300000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"sourcePaths\":[\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/spec.md\",\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/plan.md\",\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md\"]}\n+{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"synthesis_complete\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"totalIterations\":5,\"answeredCount\":5,\"totalQuestions\":5,\"stopReason\":\"converged\",\"convergenceReport\":{\"trend\":[0.92,0.78,0.52,0.34,0.12],\"compositeStopScore\":0.7,\"legalStopGates\":\"pass\",\"graphGates\":\"not_applicable\",\"qualityGuards\":\"pass\"},\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T05:36:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1}\n\nIndex: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4/deltas/iter-001.jsonl\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-dee