{"type":"text","timestamp":1783487094698,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66afffetpkX52bffjbY3h","part":{"id":"prt_f401d0325001pF7Bih2EF92N1o","messageID":"msg_f401c6b07001p1kIheGJdrUY5t","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66afffetpkX52bffjbY3h","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n- Execute detached `deep-research` fan-out lineage `gpt55-fast-4` validating the `deep-loop-runtime` + `deep-loop-workflows` merge into `system-deep-loop`.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Write only under `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4`.\n- Do not run `resolveArtifactRoot`; bind `artifact_dir` directly to `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir`.\n- Detached OpenCode lineage, not parent self-invocation.\n- Run `phase_init`, `phase_main_loop` to legal convergence or max 10, then `phase_synthesis`.\n- Final output required: `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-4`.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Loaded `deep-research` skill, command docs, YAML workflow, state/convergence references.\n- Confirmed lineage was fresh except `.executor-state/`.\n- Read parent/child specs for `052-deep-loop-unification` and live runtime/workflow/advisor/agent/plugin files.\n- Chose in-line execution instead of recursively launching `opencode run`.\n- Created lineage subdirs: `iterations/`, `deltas/`, `prompts/`.\n- Wrote:\n  - `deep-research-config.json`\n  - `deep-research-state.jsonl`\n  - `deltas/iter-001.jsonl` through `deltas/iter-005.jsonl`\n\n### In Progress\n- Human-readable iteration files and synthesis artifacts still need writing.\n- `deep-research-state.jsonl` already records convergence/synthesis_complete, but markdown/registry/dashboard outputs are incomplete.\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Runtime should nest as infrastructure under `system-deep-loop/runtime`, not become a `mode-registry` workflow mode.\n- Keep lightweight `system-spec-kit` tooling-borrow path repair; do not bundle full dependency/tooling decoupling into the structural merge.\n- Reference migration must be staged and field-scoped, not blind repo-wide replacement.\n- `fallback-router.ts` wiring should remain optional/non-blocking; if wired, model fallback policy belongs in `fanout-run.cjs`, not hardcoded in generic `fanout-pool.cjs`.\n\n## Next Steps\n- Write `iterations/iteration-001.md` through `iterations/iteration-005.md`.\n- Write `deep-research-strategy.md`.\n- Write `deep-research-findings-registry.json`.\n- Write `deep-research-dashboard.md`.\n- Write `resource-map.md`.\n- Write final `research.md` synthesis.\n- Read back/validate only files inside the lineage artifact dir.\n- Output `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-4`.\n\n## Critical Context\n- Session id: `fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01`.\n- Executor: `cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast`.\n- Memory MCP failed non-blocking: `MCP error -32000: Connection closed`.\n- Spec-level `resource-map.md` was absent.\n- Convergence modeled after 5 iterations with `newInfoRatio`: `[0.92, 0.78, 0.52, 0.34, 0.12]`; stop reason recorded as `converged`.\n- Key finding: add `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-ai-council/scripts/replay-graph-from-artifacts.cjs` to internal path-repair scope.\n- `deep-loop-runtime/package.json` owns runtime deps, but `typecheck` and `tsconfig.json` still borrow `system-spec-kit` paths.\n- Advisor hardcodes old identity in `MERGED_DEEP_SKILL_ID = 'deep-loop-workflows'` and registry path drift guard.\n- `fallback-router.ts` is tested but effectively zero-caller; `fanout-pool.cjs` currently retries same item/model.\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4`: only writable boundary.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4/deep-research-config.json`: initialized lineage config.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4/deep-research-state.jsonl`: append-only state with 5 iterations and convergence event.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4/deltas/iter-001.jsonl`: structural-layout findings.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4/deltas/iter-002.jsonl`: tooling-borrow findings.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4/deltas/iter-003.jsonl`: external-reference migration findings.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4/deltas/iter-004.jsonl`: fallback-router findings.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4/deltas/iter-005.jsonl`: convergence/closeout findings.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/package.json`: dependency/tooling-borrow evidence.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tsconfig.json`: `typeRoots` path evidence.\n- `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/lib/scorer/aliases.ts`: advisor merged-skill constant/projection evidence.\n- `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tests/routing-registry-drift-guard.vitest.ts`: hardcoded registry path evidence.","time":{"start":1783487071013,"end":1783487094694},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_08f8d49fe486a9d2016a4dda5f00748191872ae6280a2f18d9","phase":"final_answer"}}}}
