{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783487122225,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66afffetpkX52bffjbY3h","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_l5es97ZEBnwJ1FvL80UVX6d9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4/deep-research-state.jsonl","offset":1,"limit":200},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4/deep-research-state.jsonl</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\"type\":\"config\",\"topic\":\"Validate and stress-test the merge design for folding deep-loop-runtime into deep-loop-workflows as system-deep-loop: structural layout, bidirectional path-coupling repair, the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow, reference migration across commands/agents/READMEs/advisor-corpus, and whether fallback-router.ts should be wired for real GLM-5.2 to MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback.\",\"maxIterations\":10,\"minIterations\":3,\"convergenceThreshold\":0.05,\"convergenceMode\":\"default\",\"stuckThreshold\":3,\"resource_map_present\":false,\"resource_map\":{\"emit\":true},\"createdAt\":\"2026-07-08T05:10:00Z\",\"specFolder\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"openai/gpt-5.5-fast\"},\"artifactDir\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4\",\"nextRunAt\":null,\"remainingDelayMs\":null}\n2: {\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"lineage_initialized\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"lineageMode\":\"new\",\"artifactDir\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-4\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T05:10:05Z\"}\n3: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":1,\"run\":1,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research execution=single_iteration\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Structural layout and identity boundaries for system-deep-loop\",\"findingsCount\":4,\"newInfoRatio\":0.92,\"noveltyJustification\":\"First pass established the target layout, one-identity invariant, and a missing internal path-repair site not listed in the staged table.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Is the target structural layout sound?\",\"Does the bidirectional path-repair table cover live internal coupling?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"The runtime-as-nested-infrastructure shape is sound if runtime remains out of mode-registry and no nested graph-metadata is retained.\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Add runtime as a mode-registry entry\",\"reason\":\"The target layout treats runtime as infrastructure, not a workflow mode.\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/spec.md:169\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T05:15:00Z\",\"durationMs\":300000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"sourcePaths\":[\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/spec.md\",\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/plan.md\",\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-ai-council/scripts/replay-graph-from-artifacts.cjs\"]}\n4: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":2,\"run\":2,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research execution=single_iteration\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"system-spec-kit tooling-borrow and runtime dependency boundary\",\"findingsCount\":4,\"newInfoRatio\":0.78,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Confirmed the plan's path repairs are necessary, while refining the wording around runtime self-containment versus TypeScript tool borrowing.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Is the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow repair scoped correctly?\",\"Should dependency decoupling be bundled into the merge?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"The package already owns runtime dependencies, but typecheck/typeRoots and system-spec-kit test discovery still need depth repair after nesting.\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Fully decouple TypeScript tooling during the structural move\",\"reason\":\"The phase docs intentionally keep decoupling out of scope so merge failures and decoupling failures remain distinguishable.\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/plan.md:99\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T05:20:00Z\",\"durationMs\":300000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"sourcePaths\":[\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/package.json\",\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tsconfig.json\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/package.json\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/vitest.config.ts\"]}\n5: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":3,\"run\":3,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research execution=single_iteration\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"External reference migration across commands, agents, READMEs, hooks, plugin, and advisor corpus\",\"findingsCount\":4,\"newInfoRatio\":0.52,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Mostly confirmed the Stage C-J sequencing, with extra emphasis on paired Python/TypeScript advisor constants and projection-hash regeneration.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Does the external migration plan cover all high-risk reference surfaces?\",\"Are advisor-corpus edits safely scoped?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"The migration plan correctly separates hardcoded constants, generated projections, compiled command contracts, prose, graph edges, and corpus rebaseline.\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Blind repository-wide replacement of old skill ids\",\"reason\":\"Advisor corpus and divergence ledger need field-scoped replacement plus accuracy rebaseline, not a text-wide rewrite.\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md:101\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T05:25:00Z\",\"durationMs\":300000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"sourcePaths\":[\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md\",\".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py\",\".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/lib/scorer/aliases.ts\",\".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tests/routing-registry-drift-guard.vitest.ts\"]}\n6: {\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"min_iterations_guard_pass\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"run\":4,\"iterationCount\":3,\"minIterations\":3,\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T05:25:05Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1}\n7: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":4,\"run\":4,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research execution=single_iteration\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Fallback-router wiring decision and fanout retry seam\",\"findingsCount\":3,\"newInfoRatio\":0.34,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Confirmed the zero-caller gap and identified a safer integration seam than putting model policy inside the generic pool primitive.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Should fallback-router.ts become a merge blocker?\",\"Where should fallback substitution be wired if the optional phase runs?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Fallback wiring should remain optional for the structural merge; if implemented, fanout-run should own model policy and pass a retry-exhausted hook to the generic pool.\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Embed a hardcoded GLM to MiMo registry directly in fanout-pool.cjs\",\"reason\":\"fanout-pool.cjs is a generic worker-pool primitive and currently only knows items, retry counts, worker, and ledger callbacks.\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/fanout-pool.cjs:418\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T05:30:00Z\",\"durationMs\":300000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-4-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"sourcePaths\":[\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/fallback-router.ts\",\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tests/unit/fallback-router.vitest.ts\",\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/fanout-pool.cjs\",\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/fanout-run.cjs\"]}\n8: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":5,\"run\":5,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research execution=single_iteration\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Final stress test, verification ordering, and residual risks\",\"findingsCount\":2,\"newInfoRatio\":0.12,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Final pass mostly consolidated prior findings; only minor sequencing risks remained after all key questions had evidence-backed answers.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"What verification gates should block closeout?\",\"Are any merge-plan risks still unresolved?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"The closeout gates need runtime tests, system-spec-kit council tests, advisor accuracy rebaseline, divergence ratchet, mirror sync, residual grep, and temporary-symlink removal before any completion claim.\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Leave compatibility symlinks through